## Polymetis Bringup Notes

Use these commands to restart Polymetis services cleanly and bring up the Franka hardware stack.

```bash
# Activate environment
conda activate polymetis-local
pkill -f run_server
pkill -f franka_panda_client
launch_robot.py robot_client=franka_hardware


conda activate polymetis-local
launch_gripper.py gripper=franka_hand


conda activate polymetis-local
python ~/fairo-franka/polymetis/polymetis/python/polymetis/franka_interface_server.py



















Start [launch_robot](https://github.com/Shenzhaolong1330/fairo-franka/blob/main/polymetis/polymetis/python/scripts/launch_robot.py), [launch_gripper](https://github.com/Shenzhaolong1330/fairo-franka/blob/main/polymetis/polymetis/python/scripts/launch_gripper.py), and [franka_interface_server](https://github.com/Shenzhaolong1330/fairo-franka/blob/main/polymetis/polymetis/python/polymetis/franka_interface_server.py) in separate terminals.

```bash
# On the NUC
python launch_robot.py robot_client=franka_hardware
python launch_gripper.py gripper=franka_hand
python franka_interface_server.py
```